orace |first1=Stephen |title=Iran reports biggest single-day jump of coronavirus deaths as president rules out quarantine |url=https://www.foxnews.com/world/iran-coronavirus-deaths-jump |publisher=Fox News Channel |accessdate=16 March 2020 |date=15 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"oxtUC\">{{cite news |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/03/coronavirus-pandemic-kill-millions-iran-200317135500255.html |title=Coronavirus pandemic 'could kill millions' in Iran |date=17 March 2020 |publisher=Al Jazeera}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"V0Gmj\">{{cite web |title=How serious is the coronavirus crisis in Iran? |url=https://news.yahoo.com/serious-coronavirus-crisis-iran-131530378.html |publisher=Yahoo! News |accessdate=23 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<!--<ref name=\"TvKyD\">{{Cite news |last=Henley |first=Jon |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/mar/18/coronavirus-lockdown-eu-belgium-germany-adopt-measures |title=More than 250m in lockdown in EU as Belgium and Germany adopt measures |date=18 March 2020 |work=The Guardian |issn=0261-3077}}</ref>-->\n\n<ref name=\"gZcpG\">{{Cite news |first1=Angela |last1=Giuffrida |first2=Lorenzo |last2=Tondo |first3=Peter |last3=Beaumont |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/mar/04/italy-orders-closure-of-schools-and-universities-due-to-coronavirus |title=Italy orders closure of all schools and universities due to coronavirus |date=4 March 2020 |work=[[The Guardian]] |access-date=4 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Kv4Ld\">{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/51808683 |title=Coronavirus: All sport in Italy suspended because of outbreak |work=[[BBC Sport]] |date=9 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SWDJe\">{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/merkel-coronavirus-germany/2020/03/11/e276252a-6399-11ea-8a8e-5c5336b32760_story.html |title=Italy ramps up coronavirus lockdown, Merkel warns virus could infect two-thirds of Germany |first1=Chico |last1=Harlan |first2=Loveday |last2=Morris |work=[[The Washington Post]] |a