ch-the-art-life-review-1201863565/|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|title=Film Review: \u2018David Lynch: The Art Life\u2019|accessdate=April 12, 2017|last=Lodge|first=Guy|date=September 17, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/archive/73rd-festival/screenings/4sept.html|publisher=[[Venice Film Festival]]|title=73rd Venice International Film Festival|accessdate=April 12, 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"rs-overview\">{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/creep-into-david-lynchs-world-in-first-art-life-trailer-w437923|work=[[Rolling Stone (magazine)|Rolling Stone]]|title=Creep Into David Lynch's World in First 'Art Life' Documentary Trailer|accessdate=April 12, 2017|last=Kreps|first=Daniel |date=September 2, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n===Executive Producer===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:50px;\" | Ref(s)\n|-\n| 1991\n| ''The Cabinet of Dr. Ramirez''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=\"allrovi\"/>\n|-\n| 1994\n| ''[[Nadja (film)|Nadja]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=\"allrovi\"/>\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[Surveillance (2008 film)|Surveillance]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=\"allrovi\"/>\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''[[My Son, My Son, What Have Ye Done?]]''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=\"allrovi\"/>\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''The Happy Worker''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{cite magazine |url=https://deadline.com/2018/08/poldark-valley-girl-josh-whitehouse-happy-worker-david-lynch-meagan-holder-1202442299/ |title= \u2018Poldark\u2019 & \u2018Valley Girl\u2019 Star Josh Whitehouse Leads Cast In \u2018The Happy Worker\u2019, David Lynch Execs |magazine=Deadline |accessdate=August 11, 2018}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===[[Concert film]]s===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:65px;\" | Director\n! scope=\"col\" style=